@startuml 03-task-lifecycle
title Single Task Lifecycle (data-status transitions)

[*] --> blocked
blocked --> ready : all deps done
ready --> in_progress : agent claims\n(set owner)
in_progress --> done : deliverable met\n(clear owner)
in_progress --> in_progress : blocker noted\n(append data-note)
done --> [*]
@enduml
